{"1416130":{"success":true,"data":{"type":"game","name":"Perfect Vermin","steam_appid":1416130,"required_age":0,"is_free":true,"dlc":[2012460],"detailed_description":"<h1>Explore the Clownpocalypse in Clown Meat!<\/h1><p>","about_the_game":"<strong>It's not violence if they're vermin.<\/strong><br>Perfect Vermin is 10-15 minute first person narrative exploration game featuring timer based puzzle elements and multiple levels. <br><br>Your task is simple, exterminate all vermin. The sledge hammer you have been provided is capable of destroying almost all office appliances and furniture that may be uncooperative. Your time is running out.<br><br><strong>Perfect Vermin was developed by Talia bob Mair and Angad Matharoo. With Sound Design by Chris Dang and Composed by Daniel Shypilov.<\/strong><br><br><br><br>Note: Perfect Vermin is not compatible with older Intel laptops and will encounter constant issues.","short_description":"Your task is simple, exterminate all vermin. The sledge hammer you have been provided is capable of destroying almost all office appliances and furniture that may be uncooperative. Your time is running out.","supported_languages":"英语","reviews":"“Taking around 15 minutes to play through, Perfect Vermin’s office smashing antics are an absolute blast. The way the normal office furniture shatters and the vermin splat when you hit them is very satisfying. The narrative is also perfectly executed, with lots of little clues about what’s really going on throughout and an ending that gives much more significance to your vermin-splatting rampage. Highly recommended.”<br>Highly recommended. – Alpha Beta Gamer<br><br>“But either way it was interesting. It's not really like. Well its actually kind of fun. Smashing stuff not hunting down the vermin, just smashing stuff in general is pretty fun. But the actual experience itself is very unique. I think that's the best compliment you could give. I'm not using it as a sarcastic unique but I mean like literally it was unique.”<br>ManlyBadassHero<br><br>“That was really intense, yeah GG Perfect Vermin, GG Matt.”<br>GG – Matt Pat (Game Theory)<br>","header_image":"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1416130\/header.jpg?t=1708109979","capsule_image":"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1416130\/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1708109979","capsule_imagev5":"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1416130\/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1708109979","website":null,"pc_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>最低配置:<\/strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>操作系统 *:<\/strong> Windows 7 64-bit<br><\/li><li><strong>处理器:<\/strong> Intel or AMD processor, 2.5 GHz<br><\/li><li><strong>内存:<\/strong> 8 GB RAM<br><\/li><li><strong>显卡:<\/strong> NVIDIA GeForce 470 GTX or AMD Radeon 6870 HD series card<br><\/li><li><strong>DirectX 版本:<\/strong> 11<br><\/li><li><strong>存储空间:<\/strong> 需要 385 MB 可用空间<\/li><\/ul>"},"mac_requirements":[],"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>最低配置:<\/strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>操作系统:<\/strong> Ubuntu Linux<br><\/li><li><strong>处理器:<\/strong> Intel or AMD processor, 2.5 GHz<br><\/li><li><strong>内存:<\/strong> 8 GB RAM<br><\/li><li><strong>显卡:<\/strong> NVIDIA GeForce 470 GTX or AMD Radeon 6870 HD series card<br><\/li><li><strong>存储空间:<\/strong> 需要 1050 MB 可用空间<\/li><\/ul>"},"developers":["Talia bob Mair","Angad Matharoo"],"publishers":["ItsTheTalia"],"package_groups":[],"platforms":{"windows":true,"mac":false,"linux":false},"categories":[{"id":2,"description":"单人"},{"id":22,"description":"Steam 成就"},{"id":18,"description":"部分支持控制器"}],"genres":[{"id":"1","description":"动作"},{"id":"25","description":"冒险"},{"id":"4","description":"休闲"},{"id":"23","description":"独立"},{"id":"37","description":"免费开玩"}],"screenshots":[{"id":0,"path_thumbnail":"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/1416130\/ss_1d9ce05f3fee276e6a04fc39919aaa95f50473af.600x338.